:0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:43:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比組爸食左留名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰陣玩ocamp已經覺得佢好型棍<br />\n完左仲對我好好<br />\n咁大個仔第一次中意人<br />\n跟住有次去廁所撞到<br />\n之後就上左房埋牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8f5f9ac7780889330247431a5e4c741583f8d28","tid":380851,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:43:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比組爸食左留名</blockquote><br />\n後唔後悔 多數食組女<br />\n<br />\n一係餓得太耐 食唔到同年既毒j<br />\n<br />\n一係player"},{"pid":"f234ddd7e8fd36c4fdc13891014f93b9000de66c","tid":380851,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:46:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>食過一個組女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nshare 下啦屌"},{"pid":"9e59ecf67eda1cd793c192a1eda8272a496730c9","tid":380851,"uid":127333,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:48:44.000Z","msg":"師兄一定好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"264a2ba57f574a118ce7e67cf67a59cbb2fccc4e","tid":380851,"uid":135160,"like":44,"dislike":0,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:51:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/215119_83179307b321b9d7344e984367cc8bf9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F215119_83179307b321b9d7344e984367cc8bf9.jpg&h=af1d347f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好咁懶又用同一個ac啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"804d0697bb0299f3e192445804a912df4ec480be","tid":380851,"uid":135445,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:53:36.000Z","msg":"我同你相遇既概率<br />\n係0同1之間<br />\n無論係偏向1定係偏向0<br />\n答案也不會是我滿意的。<br />\n概率都是騙人騙自己既工具<br />\n因為<br />\n無論係0.999抑或0.001<br />\n你是幸運的<br />\n0.001也可以是1<br />\n同樣地，0.999也可以是<br />\n說到底<br />\n一切的概率都是0.5<br />\n明明只是一條單純的問題<br />\n世人卻妄想以數學解構天機<br />\n以概率證明自己的不幸<br />\n抑或幸運。<br />\n說到底<br />\n無論是男是女<br />\n還是屌不屌到女<br />\n還是食不食到組媽<br />\n還是，與你能否成為密友<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一切都是概率。</span></span>"},{"pid":"fbf8dec29a11504de0265ce971d04b13ae3c022c","tid":380851,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:55:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/30/215119_83179307b321b9d7344e984367cc8bf9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F30%2F215119_83179307b321b9d7344e984367cc8bf9.jpg&h=af1d347f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔好咁懶又用同一個ac啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再起前啲底啦屌<br />\n<br />\n就grad啦我"},{"pid":"3696060c488d84092dd39867755d726498133ef8","tid":380851,"uid":69382,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:55:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>比組爸食左留名</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nSame<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嗰陣玩ocamp已經覺得佢好型棍<br />\n完左仲對我好好<br />\n咁大個<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">仔</span></span>第一次中意人<br />\n跟住有次去廁所撞到<br />\n之後就上左房埋牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"b3dd7797a0a0fe11d841b9d77ac9ef57351f64d3","tid":380851,"uid":54581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-30T13:55:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>師兄一定好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n普通樣"},{"pid":"6644dbb3b2a92f3c5c407658c1edb38b73f52336","tid":380851,"uid":6